ury-2024-3601011">韩国流行音乐将首次出现在音乐节上，</a> Pledis 男孩乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seventeen">SEVENTEEN</a>在金字塔阶段。 </p><figure id="attachment_3768718" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768718" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768718" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/glastonbury-gates-2024@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节第一天，游客在沃西农场 (Worthy Farm) 早上 8 点开门前排队" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/glastonbury-gates-2024@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/glastonbury-gates-2024@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/glastonbury-gates-2024@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/glastonbury-gates-2024@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/glastonbury-gates-2024@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/glastonbury-gates-2024@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768718" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的大门已正式打开。图片来源：Leon Neal/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>今年演出的其他艺人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Burna Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anne-marie">Anne-Marie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/confidence-man">Confidence Man</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/disclosure">Disclosure</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camila-cabello">Camila Cabello</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="